description:
On March 13, in Switzerland the Canton Jura announced 
-the closure of all schools (compulsory and post-compulsory) from March 16 till April 4, 2020. There will be no more face-to-face teaching but the work of students will continue remote. Apprentices in dual training will be 100% active in business;
-the closure of childcare facilities. The crèches and UAPE (school children day care) will however remain open for parents with a work contract in health and social institutions;
